expression:
Loot #2157 was wash-traded
ten times between by 0xB7639A and 0x996665 for 1 ETH
between 2022-08-10T12:11:14Z and 2022-08-11T03:25:36Z.
Shortly after, it was sold by 0xB7639A to 0xcc8990, and
the same wash trading behavior happened again between
0xcc8990 and 0xBF1eD4, and more address pairs. Within a
day, 178 transactions transpired back and forth at nearly the
same price, and the domain names of sellers and buyers were
highly similar, all in the form of Chinese license plates.
